'''M82 X-1'''是位於星系[[雪茄星系|M82]]中的{{link-en|超亮X射線源|Ultraluminous X-ray source}}。它是一個[[中等質量黑洞|中等質量黑洞]]的候選者，精確的質量估計在100到1000太陽質量之間<ref>{{Cite journal|arxiv=astro-ph/0409416|title=Is M82 X-1 Really an Intermediate-Mass Black Hole? X-Ray Spectral and Timing Evidence|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|volume=614|issue=2|pages=L113–L116|doi=10.1086/425736|year=2004|last1=Fiorito|first1=Ralph|last2=Titarchuk|first2=Lev|bibcode = 2004ApJ...614L.113F|s2cid=10183683}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|arxiv=1607.03903|title=A Broadband X-Ray Spectral Study of the Intermediate-mass Black Hole Candidate M82 X-1 with NuSTAR, Chandra, and Swift|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|volume=829|issue=1|pages=28|bibcode=2016ApJ...829...28B|last1=Brightman|first1=Murray|last2=Harrison|first2=Fiona A.|last3=Barret|first3=Didier|last4=Davis|first4=Shane W.|last5=Fürst|first5=Felix|last6=Madsen|first6=Kristin K.|last7=Middleton|first7=Matthew|last8=Miller|first8=Jon M.|last9=Stern|first9=Daniel|last10=Tao|first10=Lian|last11=Walton|first11=Dominic J.|year=2016|doi=10.3847/0004-637X/829/1/28|s2cid=19765183}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://earthsky.org/space/strange-case-of-m82-x-1-a-rare-midsize-black-hole|title=Strange case of M82 X-1: A rare midsize black hole {{!}} EarthSky.org|website=earthsky.org|date=19 August 2014|language=en-US|access-date=2019-03-03|archive-date=2021-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211102005543/https://earthsky.org/space/strange-case-of-m82-x-1-a-rare-midsize-black-hole/}}</ref>。它是已知最亮的超視距X星之一，其亮度超過了恒星質量天體的[[愛丁頓光度|愛丁頓極限]]。
